[domain]
# incomplete information
initially plantAlive

waterPlant causes plantWatered
waterPlant causes !plantAlive if plantWatered
wait causes !plantWatered
wait causes !plantAlive if !plantWatered

waterPlant costs 1
wait costs 9

[queries]
# we can tell the plant will die even though we have incomplete information
!plantAlive after wait, wait
!plantAlive after waterPlant, waterPlant

plantAlive after waterPlant, wait, waterPlant, wait
!plantAlive after waterPlant, wait, waterPlant, wait
waterPlant, wait, waterPlant, wait executable with cost 20
wait, wait, wait, wait executable with cost 18
waterPlant, waterPlant, waterPlant, waterPlant executable with exact cost 2